  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c20a5a1acd1eee477b10483160c3c3fe, type: 3}
  m_Name: DemonData_AdmiralFortran
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: LSG::LSG.DemonData_AdmiralFortran
  demonName: Admiral Fortran
  canDateDemonMultipleTimes: 0
  introDialogue: 'His demon-leather uniform is sharp, his demon-bone combadge glitters
    with impossible colors, his combination null-laser/dueling saber quietly cuts
    a rift in space behind him.  "Admiral''s Log: I seem to have been transported
    from my voidship.  In all my years sailing the hellstars, I''ve never experienced
    such a thing."


    He quickly notices you and levels his weapon in your direction. 
    "You say it is the custom of this world to go on a ''date'' in response to such
    a summoning?  Fascinating."

'
  minimumPowerLevel: 10
  maximumPowerLevel: 25
  outcome: '"We shall follow the customs of my world, instead. As such, your home
    is now annexed by the Ceuterian Dynasty.  However, you are entitled to protection
    against incursions by the Talametran Corsairs, in exchange for a 1.6% tax benefitting
    the Ceuterian Dynasty. You will be satisfied by this deal," the handsome Admiral
    states matter-of-factly before fading away in a silhouette of swirling glittering
    stars.'
  boon: The next time you would play 8 or more white points of cards, instead shuffle
    the last read white card back into the deck (you get an oopsie freebie redo)
  bane: Lose 1 Tape (if the player has a tape banked)
  boonBaneDialogue: "Admiral Fortran's Blessing has prevented an incursion by the
    Talametran Corsairs, whoever they are, and this dagger is left unread. \n\nAdmiral
    Fortran's Curse has taxed away one of your Tape for the Ceuterian Dynasty."
  dateOutcome: 'He is both a gentleman and an enthusiastic participant in your strange
    Hyu-Man culture, equally able to dazzle on the ballroom or night club dance floor. 
    He says he merely wants to comport himself according to the local customs.


    He''s
    very interested in your home life, your career, your most exploitable resources,
    but in such an earnest way that you find it cute.  You thought suggesting a hike
    would interest him, but you underestimated just how into it he would be: all
    his experience with planetary explorations make him really hard to keep up with,
    although you''re getting a great view of his calves from behind.'
  demonSprite: {fileID: 4865967287530129530, guid: c885b2bc9c8edb5239b2ebb3606d1ac9, type: 3}
